Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:04.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然辞职…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:08.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻他… 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是图书馆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:41.88,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛し…愛し合うのさ もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:41.88,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱…更加地相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:48.14,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激しい渇きに狂いそう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:48.14,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激烈的饥渴让我发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:57.33,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目を閉じて 罪深き くちづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:57.33,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闭上眼睛 罪孽深重的接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:08.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}お前の匂い 狂わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:08.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的味道 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.05,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真夜中に目覚めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.05,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在半夜里睁开眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.08,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}狂気 愛 飲み干す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.08,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}把爱与疯狂喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.43,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.43,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}过来 到我的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.55,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.55,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那边的黑暗是苦涩的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.50,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の惑い 揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.50,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你在迷惘 在动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて永遠になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}最终将永远无法解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:34.45,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「こっちの闇は甘いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:34.45,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「这边的黑暗是甘甜的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:40.47,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕は深く 突き刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:40.47,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我狠狠地刺进最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.53,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.53,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}过来 到我的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那边的黑暗是苦涩的哦」
